Peter O'Brien (actor) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Peter_O%27Brien_(actor) 0 Peter O'Brien (born 25 March 1960) is an Australian actor, best known for his role as an original cast member in 1985 of Australian soap opera Neighbours as Shane Ramsay.
